parameters.name: OrganizationId
parameters.description: The organization that contains the group.

parameters.name: GroupId
parameters.description: The identifier of the group to be deleted. The identifier can be the GroupId, or Groupname. The following identity formats are available: Group ID: 12345678-1234-1234-1234-123456789012 or S-1-1-12-1234567890-123456789-123456789-1234 Group name: group.
